.TH HYPRLAND\-WELCOME 1 "2025-11-20" "hyprland-guiutils 0.2.1" "Hyprland Ecosystem"
.SH NAME
hyprland\-welcome \- Hyprland welcome and setup wizard
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hyprland\-welcome
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hyprland\-welcome
is a multi\-tab welcome and setup wizard for new Hyprland users.
It guides users through initial configuration including selecting a default
terminal emulator, file manager, and application launcher.
.PP
The wizard detects installed applications and presents available choices
for each category.
Detected terminals include kitty, alacritty, wezterm, foot, konsole,
and gnome\-terminal.
Detected file managers include dolphin, thunar, pcmanfm, nautilus,
and nemo.
Detected launchers include hyprlauncher, fuzzel, wofi, rofi, anyrun,
and tofi\-drun.
.PP
The window class is
.BR hyprland\-welcome .
.SH OPTIONS
None.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR Hyprland (1)
.SH AUTHOR
The Hyprland Development Team
